quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  15,45,"Pellet, gom…óu…ìe …ìen wonii e aljannaaji e …ìulli"
  15,46,"Naatiree …ói e kisial, ko on hoolii…ìe"
  15,47,"Men …óoofi kala ko woni e …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe e konnaagu(cokotaagal): …ìe wonti musi…ó…ìe fewtondir…ìe e dan…óe"
  15,48,"Tampere he…ìataa …ìe ton, …ìe wonah kadi yaltintee …ìe ton"
  15,49,"Yeetito jeyaa…ìe Am …ìen, ko Min woni Haforoowo, Hinnotoo…óo On"
  15,50,"e wonnde lepte Am …óen, ko …óen woni lepte muusu…óe …óen"
  15,51,Yeetito …ìe kadi fii ho…ì…ìe Ibraahiima …ìen
  15,52,"Tuma …ìe naatunoo ka makko …ìe wi'i: \"Salaam (Kisiyee mon)\". O maaki: \"Menen ko men …óen∆¥ii …ìe on"
  15,53,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Wata a faay, menen me…óen wewlinire […ìi…ó…óo] gorko ganndo"
  15,54,"O maaki: \"E on wewliniray lam […óum] e hoore ko mi nawyi kon? E ko wewlinirton mi"
  15,55,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Men wewlinirii ma goonga, wata a jeye e ta∆¥ii…ìe …ìen"
  15,56,"O maaki: \"Ko hommbo ta∆¥otoo e yurmeende Joomi mun nden, si wanaa majju…ìe …ìen"
  15,57,"O maaki: \"Ko woni fii mon, onon …ìee imminaa…ìe"
  15,58,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Menen men nulaa ko e yim…ìe bom…ìe"
  15,59,"si wanaa …ìeynguure Luuti nden, pellet ko men da…óndoo…ìe …ìe denndaangal"
  15,60,"si wanaa debbo makko on\". Men hoddirii on …óon ko jeyaa…óo e halketee…ìe …ìen"